---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Church - Klesis Christian Fellowship">
	<section class="hero">
		<div class="container">
			<h1>Our Church Community</h1>
			<p class="hero-subtitle">Discover what it means to be part of the body of Christ</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="about-church-section">
		<div class="container">
			<h2>What We Believe About Church</h2>
			<div class="belief-content">
				<p>
					The church isn't just a building or an organization - it's a living community of believers 
					who gather together to worship God, grow in faith, and serve others. As a campus ministry, 
					we're part of the larger body of Christ, connecting students with both local congregations 
					and the global Christian community.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="values-section">
		<div class="container">
			<h2>Our Core Values</h2>
			<div class="values-grid">
				<div class="value-card">
					<div class="value-icon">üìñ</div>
					<h3>Biblical Foundation</h3>
					<p>
						We base our beliefs and practices on Scripture, studying God's Word together 
						to understand His truth and apply it to our lives as students.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="value-card">
					<div class="value-icon">ü§ù</div>
					<h3>Authentic Community</h3>
					<p>
						We believe in genuine relationships where we can be ourselves, support each other, 
						and grow together in faith through the challenges of college life.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="value-card">
					<div class="value-icon">‚ù§Ô∏è</div>
					<h3>Loving Service</h3>
					<p>
						Following Christ's example, we seek to serve our campus, local community, 
						and world with compassion and practical action.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="value-card">
					<div class="value-icon">üåü</div>
					<h3>Transforming Grace</h3>
					<p>
						We celebrate the life-changing power of God's grace, believing that everyone 
						can experience forgiveness, hope, and new life in Jesus Christ.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="gathering-section">
		<div class="container">
			<h2>How We Gather</h2>
			<div class="gathering-grid">
				<div class="gathering-item">
					<h3>üéµ Weekly Worship</h3>
					<p>
						Join us for our main weekly gathering featuring contemporary worship music, 
						biblical teaching, and time for fellowship. It's a highlight of our week together!
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="gathering-item">
					<h3>üìö Small Groups</h3>
					<p>
						Connect more deeply through smaller Bible study groups where we dive into Scripture, 
						share prayer requests, and build lasting friendships.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="gathering-item">
					<h3>üçï Social Events</h3>
					<p>
						From game nights to outdoor adventures, we love spending time together outside of 
						formal meetings, building community through shared experiences.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="gathering-item">
					<h3>üôè Prayer & Support</h3>
					<p>
						We're here for each other through the ups and downs of college life, offering 
						prayer, encouragement, and practical support when needed.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="local-church-section">
		<div class="container">
			<h2>Connection to Local Churches</h2>
			<div class="church-content">
				<p>
					While Klesis provides community during your college years, we also encourage students 
					to connect with local churches in the San Francisco area. We believe in the importance 
					of being part of a broader church family that includes people of all ages and life stages.
				</p>
				<div class="church-features">
					<div class="feature">
						<h4>üèõÔ∏è Church Visits</h4>
						<p>We organize visits to various local churches to help students find their church home.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="feature">
						<h4>ü§≤ Service Opportunities</h4>
						<p>Partner with local congregations in community service and outreach programs.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="feature">
						<h4>üë• Mentorship</h4>
						<p>Connect with older believers who can provide wisdom and guidance for your faith journey.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="join-section">
		<div class="container">
			<h2>Ready to Join Our Community?</h2>
			<p class="join-text">
				Whether you're exploring faith for the first time or looking to grow deeper in your relationship 
				with God, there's a place for you in our community.
			</p>
			<div class="join-actions">
				<a href="/connect" class="primary-button">Get Connected</a>
				<a href="/statement-of-faith" class="secondary-button">Our Beliefs</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	.container {
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 0 2rem;
	}

	/* Hero Section */
	.hero {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #059669 0%, #047857 100%);
		color: white;
		padding: 5rem 0;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.hero h1 {
		font-size: 3rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.hero-subtitle {
		font-size: 1.3rem;
		opacity: 0.9;
		max-width: 600px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	/* About Church Section */
	.about-church-section {
		padding: 5rem 0;
		background: white;
	}

	.about-church-section h2 {
		text-align: center;
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		color: #1e293b;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
	}

	.belief-content p {
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		line-height: 1.8;
		color: #475569;
		max-width: 900px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		text-align: center;
	}

	/* Values Section */
	.values-section {
		padding: 5rem 0;
		background: #f8fafc;
	}

	.values-section h2 {
		text-align: center;
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		color: #1e293b;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
	}

	.values-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.value-card {
		background: white;
		padding: 2.5rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
		text-align: center;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
		transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
	}

	.value-card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-5px);
		box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
	}

	.value-icon {
		font-size: 3rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.value-card h3 {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		color: #1e293b;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.value-card p {
		color: #64748b;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	/* Gathering Section */
	.gathering-section {
		padding: 5rem 0;
		background: white;
	}

	.gathering-section h2 {
		text-align: center;
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		color: #1e293b;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
	}

	.gathering-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.gathering-item {
		padding: 2rem;
		border-left: 4px solid #059669;
		background: #f0fdf4;
		border-radius: 8px;
	}

	.gathering-item h3 {
		font-size: 1.3rem;
		color: #1e293b;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.gathering-item p {
		color: #475569;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	/* Local Church Section */
	.local-church-section {
		padding: 5rem 0;
		background: #f1f5f9;
	}

	.local-church-section h2 {
		text-align: center;
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		color: #1e293b;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
	}

	.church-content p {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		line-height: 1.8;
		color: #475569;
		text-align: center;
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto 3rem auto;
	}

	.church-features {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.feature {
		background: white;
		padding: 2rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
		text-align: center;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
	}

	.feature h4 {
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		color: #1e293b;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.feature p {
		color: #64748b;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		line-height: 1.5;
	}

	/* Join Section */
	.join-section {
		padding: 5rem 0;
		background: white;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.join-section h2 {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		color: #1e293b;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.join-text {
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		color: #475569;
		max-width: 700px;
		margin: 0 auto 3rem auto;
		line-height: 1.7;
	}

	.join-actions {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1rem;
		justify-content: center;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
	}

	.primary-button,
	.secondary-button {
		padding: 1rem 2rem;
		border-radius: 8px;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: 600;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
		display: inline-block;
	}

	.primary-button {
		background: #059669;
		color: white;
	}

	.primary-button:hover {
		background: #047857;
		transform: translateY(-2px);
	}

	.secondary-button {
		background: white;
		color: #059669;
		border: 2px solid #059669;
	}

	.secondary-button:hover {
		background: #059669;
		color: white;
	}

	/* Mobile Styles */
	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.container {
			padding: 0 1rem;
		}

		.hero {
			padding: 4rem 0;
		}

		.hero h1 {
			font-size: 2.5rem;
		}

		.about-church-section,
		.values-section,
		.gathering-section,
		.local-church-section,
		.join-section {
			padding: 3rem 0;
		}

		.values-grid,
		.gathering-grid,
		.church-features {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.join-actions {
			flex-direction: column;
			align-items: center;
		}

		.primary-button,
		.secondary-button {
			width: 100%;
			max-width: 300px;
		}
	}
</style>
